me type (refund/green/red), greenCount, redCount, pythPrice.price, openPrice |\n| **After Settlement** | entriesPerSide arrays, winning player list (or all players for refund), settle tx signature |\n| **On Restart** | Can recover activeRound via discriminator scan + phase check |\n\n### **Key Constraints**\n\n- Round PDA seeds: `[\"cc_round\", roundId]` (line 533)\n- Phase values: Open=0, Settled=1, Refunded=2 (line 49-54)\n- Outcome values: Pending=0, Green=1, Red=2, Refund=3 (line 57-64)\n- Clock ticks every minute, aligned 2s after minute boundary (lines 40-41, 88-92)"}],"totalDurationMs":38205,"totalTokens":52113,"totalToolUseCount":6,"usage":{"input_tokens":6,"cache_creation_input_tokens":13909,"cache_read_input_tokens":37080,"output_tokens":1118,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":13909},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
